<div id="ftn114">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="#_ftnref114" name="_ftn114"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="Caractredenotedebasdepage"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[114]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a>          cf. Françoise BREYNAERT, <i>L’arbre de vie, symbole central de la spiritualité de Saint Louis-Marie de Montfort, </i>éditions Paroles et silence 2006, p. 330-334.</p>
