<div id="ftn117">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="#_ftnref117" name="_ftn117"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="Caractredenotedebasdepage"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[117]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a><span lang="IT">          Le texte latin dit : « <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Cum</span> Unigenito suo <span style="text-decoration: underline;">con</span>doluit »</span></p>
